Agency Name: Department of Health and Mental Hygiene
Resolution Description: The Department of Health and Mental Hygiene will review your complaint within 24 hours.  Complaints of this type usually result in complainant contact and/or inspection by the agency. Initial status will be available 14 days after the date of your complaint by calling 311. If you are experiencing medical symptoms, please seek medical attention or consult the NYC Poison Control Center which can be reached through 311.   Please note your Service Request number for future reference.
